title: Latinas in Tech is hosting its 2nd annual startup competition for Latina-founded companies, with a $20000 top prize - The Business Journals
content: Latinas in Tech is hosting its 2nd annual startup competition for Latina-founded companies, with a $20000 top prize  The Business Journals
